short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: View your browsing history as a tree

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Your browser history is your mind map. The journey of how you got to your information can be as important as the information itself. You want to know what you already read, what you tried that didn't work, and how you ended up on the page that you did.
